title: WI-FI in all common areas, Directly across the street from Amazon
posting_body: ['Met Tower', '1942 Westlake Avenue, Seattle, WA, 98101', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 71', 'OR Text', '71', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', 'WELCOME TO MET TOWER', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath, approximately 1458 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Met Tower delivers the best of both worlds – the comforts of your own home while providing all the luxury and convenience of a 5-star hotel.', 'Not enough?', 'You will also enjoy a host of amenities exclusive for residents; private balcony/patio, 24-hour personalized Concierge Service, Indoor Swimming Pool, Spa, Fitness Center and more.', 'Our community is located in the heart of Seattle (98101), we are directly across the street from Amazon so there is no better commute for all you Amazonians!', 'Did we mention that we are in walking distance to some of the most amazing restaurants and retail in all of Seattle, well we are!', 'We also have some of the most convenient transportation within blocks of our community!', 'If that isn’t your style, then our convenient parking garage will be perfect to keep your car at your fingertips to hit the open road.', 'Met Tower goes even further to provide comfort, convenience and luxury for our residents by providing a gorgeous outdoor terrace, dog run, business & entertainment centers and billiards room.', 'You can’t beat the 360 degrees of breathtaking views; from Elliot Bay and the Olympics to the Cascades, each one of our homes offer views that rival any Instagram account and makes you want to have your iPhone on the ready for the next time the sun sets.', 'Pet Policy', "BFF's Welcomed!", 'Monthly Pet Rent of $50.', 'We have no weight limit restriction.', 'Certain breed restrictions apply.', 'Call today for more details!', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday-Sunday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'peGB2CnCSlyf']
